This is a companion of PR https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/42953.
Goals are:
   * refresh the `streamDQMGPUvsCPU` unit tests files in order to include also Pixel FED errors for `SiPixelPhase1RawDataErrorComparator`;
   * add `streamDQM` file for `sistrip_appror sistrip_approx_dqm_sourceclient-live` unit test;
   * update `README` file

**Note to reviewers: to pass tests this PR needs to be tested with https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/42953**
